{"tid":2366783,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–燒呀燒讓脂肪燒","createTime":"2021-01-14T21:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T11:34:12.000Z","uid":38861,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"644a562543fe25d9db946f56c76cdcf91e6b6844","tid":2366783,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:29:37.000Z","msg":"食物內含的油脂，經過腸道消化後便會進入血液循環系統。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ea0LZcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEa0LZcc.jpg&h=1e069f0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在血管內，油脂會與蛋白質組成名為TRL的結構，繼而送到身體各部份。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）油脂雖能為細胞帶來豐盛的能量，但同時亦能聚積在白色脂肪裡頭，加劇糖尿病的發生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v7A8cxf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv7A8cxf.jpg&h=63598118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此外，它們亦能聚積在血管裡頭，阻塞通道，造就動脈硬化。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）在這一方面，啡色脂肪能夠有效地將油脂等營養轉化成熱能。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FHzABYY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFHzABYY.png&h=a1ba25a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而擁有啡色脂肪的人，血糖及血液油脂的份量亦相對地比沒有啡色脂肪的人為低。<br />\n<br />\n啡色脂肪促使血糖及血脂降低，能減低患上糖尿病的風險。<br />\n有論說是認為啡色脂肪把糖份及油燃燒消耗而成，亦有論說是啡色脂肪造就的荷爾蒙轉變或免疫系統轉變所致。<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，如果能找出一道安全而具有效率提升啡色脂肪的方法，將必有莫大的治療價值。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVQomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=6a81babe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVQomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=2e85fbc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於WhatsApp/Facebook等問題，IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-020-1126-7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41591-020-1126-7&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVQomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=f101918a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-020-1126-7</a>"},{"pid":"15a5ee88161e013b98ee2e3f5f413a019974a239","tid":2366783,"uid":34119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:33:46.000Z","msg":"IG將不會再作更新<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d41c7eed465ff5245513bebe954fbd7756b0d99","tid":2366783,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"15a5ee88161e013b98ee2e3f5f413a019974a239","tid":2366783,"uid":34119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:33:46.000Z","msg":"IG將不會再作更新<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:39:38.000Z","msg":"想轉VERO，但無繁體中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a47d60697cdba8a2665adc53502e2e5158d1af9","tid":2366783,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d41c7eed465ff5245513bebe954fbd7756b0d99","tid":2366783,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"15a5ee88161e013b98ee2e3f5f413a019974a239","tid":2366783,"uid":34119,"like":1,"dislike"