ss=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:41:37.000Z","msg":"vero 都係睇定啲先<br />\n<br />\nbtw問唔問得隻肺炎嘅問題?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:43:04.000Z","msg":"點解唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過大概10分鐘後我就訓，太長的話我訓醒先再覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:44:37.000Z","msg":"其實隻病毒係咪airborne傳?<br />\n係咪得n95 up先有效?<br />\n熱同UV可唔可以deactivate 佢?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12437893bd8ec7b67ea1fab9c3f9a9160c4f451c","tid":2366783,"uid":38861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bdd5b6f87c4e4bbaffec918ac1f8c6b7ef83bf37","tid":2366783,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eb238c7eb0ab3bdb585fe513d7a1aefef0cba9e","tid":2366783,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a47d60697cdba8a2665adc53502e2e5158d1af9","tid":2366783,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:41:37.000Z","msg":"vero 都係睇定啲先<br />\n<br />\nbtw問唔問得隻肺炎嘅問題?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:43:04.000Z","msg":"點解唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過大概10分鐘後我就訓，太長的話我訓醒先再覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:44:37.000Z","msg":"其實隻病毒係咪airborne傳?<br />\n係咪得n95 up先有效?<br />\n熱同UV可唔可以deactivate 佢?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:54:47.000Z","msg":"唔知係唔係airbone。<br />\n<br />\nn95最有效，唔係先有效。主流認為病毒要黏附口水或其他液體先可以傳播開去，口罩隔到水份同阻隔一定大小物質通過就應該可以擋得到病毒入侵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n熱同紫外線可以deactivate佢。<br />\n<br />\n武肺病毒有望在夏天減慢傳播？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1933626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1933626</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7d22fd8a5a6e47d08550cd447d1cd3aa03a1d10b","tid":2366783,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12437893bd8ec7b67ea1fab9c3f9a9160c4f451c","tid":2366783,"uid":38861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bdd5b6f87c4e4bbaffec918ac1f8c6b7ef83bf37","tid":2366783,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eb238c7eb0ab3bdb585fe513d7a1aefef0cba9e","tid":2366783,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:43:04.000Z","msg":"點解唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過大概10分鐘後我就訓，太長的話我訓醒先再覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:44:37.000Z","msg":"其實隻病毒係咪airborne傳?<br />\n係咪得n95 up先有效?<br />\n熱同UV可唔可以deactivate 佢?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:54:47.000Z","msg":"唔知係唔係airbone。<br />\n<br />\nn95最有效，唔係先有效。主流認為病毒要黏附口水或其他液體先可以傳播開去，口罩隔到水份同阻隔一定大小物質通過就應該可以擋得到病毒入侵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n熱同紫外線可以deactivate佢。<br />\n<br />\n武肺病毒有望在夏天減慢傳播？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1933626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1933626</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T22:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感謝 閣下先休息再later 睇我另一個technical問題<br />\n3m 個6035 filters 由官方指可以last足一個pandemic wave, 而又只係因為breathing difficulties 先要換.<br />\n咁淨係睇最尾嗰句又話要睇infection control reason換, 但係係for medical staff reference, 我想知如果係日常 非高傳染風險場所 用咗成個秋冬春wave 係咪最好都係要換filer?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.co.uk/intl/uk/ohes/segments/healthcare/(9666a)OH_ReusableTechBulletin_lft.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.co.uk%2Fintl%2Fuk%2Fohes%2Fsegments%2Fhealthcare%2F%289666a%29OH_ReusableTechBulletin_lft.pdf&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVQomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=31e2f13e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.co.uk/intl/uk/ohes/segments/healthcare/(9666a)OH_ReusableTechBulletin_lft.pdf</a><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">A &ndash; Filters should be changed when they become clogged with<br />\nparticulate contaminant. The wearer can determine when this occurs as<br />\nit becomes harder to breathe through the filters.<br />\nThe filters are designed to filter out particles in industrial conditions<br />\nand in concentrations much higher than is likely to be encountered in<br />\na pandemic situation. It is therefore expected that one set of filters will<br />\ncover at least one pandemic wave, after which <span class=\"red\">they should be replaced<br />\nfor infection control reasons</span>.</span>"},{"pid":"6083a0412aa8f4ec087ee434ca0640bc068081c5","tid":2366783,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:02:36.000Z","msg":"成日都老鍊咁早出文嘅"},{"pid":"71a6adf17fdfc0681ebac56b29a3a8874dbb2ff9","tid":2366783,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T03:13:05.000Z","msg":"薯仔係咪返左去啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6faf51c7f39a0a1ca5bc94f0093d46c98b62fc63","tid":2366783,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5511ddea3b55cf2908305b46d801d8770308d013","tid":2366783,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:03:02.000Z","msg":"點先可以減脂<br />\nTdee食少咗都減唔到"},{"pid":"1ed52f63b2f42a8cbac570784049d114adabf23b","tid":2366783,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"